# DX12 playloop script: warfront pressure validation
page.goto warfront
engine.config war-radius 7
engine.config reinforcements 3
engine.config population-cap 160
actor.spawn banana combat 1.5 0.5
actor.spawn bean wildlife 2.5 -0.5
engine.config snapshot-interval 2
page.tick 2
expect.team-count banana gte 2
expect.team-count bean gte 2
expect.metric controllers gte 4
expect.mode banana hold-line
expect.mode bean hold-line
snapshot pressure-baseline
note pressure_baseline_validated
